---
title: Saucy Italian Beef Meatball Sub with Parmesan & Fries
description: The sub sandwich is the king of sandwiches. Packed to bursting with saucy meatballs and sprinkled in Parmesan cheese, this
particular sub wears the crown with ease and grace. We bow before the might of this delicious meal!
